---
// AboutLicense component - Regulatory compliance section
// Based on AboutPrinciple component design
---

<section>
  <div class="bg-theme-light relative py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container grid gap-x-10 gap-y-10 overflow-hidden md:gap-y-20 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:place-items-center">
      {/* Left Column - Image */}
      <div class="lg:max-w-2xl" data-aos="fade-right-sm">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
          <img 
            src="/images/about-us/MMC Financial Securities Commission.webp" 
            alt="MMC Financial 马来西亚证券委员会注册证书" 
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
          />
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4 text-center">
            马来西亚证券委员会公共注册系统 - MMC FP Sdn Bhd 注册信息
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {/* Right Column - Content */}
      <div class="lg:max-w-2xl">
        <div data-aos="fade-up-sm">
          {/* Subtitle */}
          <span class="bg-primary/5 border-secondary text-primary mb-2.5 inline-block rounded-full border px-5 py-px">
            监管合规认证
          </span>
          {/* Main Title */}
          <h2 class="text-h3 text-inherit">
            持牌金融机构，合规经营
          </h2>
        </div>
        {/* Description */}
        <div data-aos="fade-up-sm" data-aos-delay="200" class="mt-6">
          <p class="text-text-default">
            MMC FP Sdn Bhd 是马来西亚证券委员会（Securities Commission Malaysia）正式授权的持牌金融机构。
            我们持有有效的资本市场服务执照（Capital Markets Services Licence），注册号码为 eCMSL/A0224/2008，
            自2008年3月28日起获得许可，专门从事财务规划服务。这确保了我们的服务符合马来西亚金融监管的最高标准，
            为客户提供安全、专业、合规的财务规划解决方案。
          </p>
        </div>
        {/* Features List */}
        <div class="divide-border-default/35 mt-8 divide-y md:mt-12">
          {/* Feature 1 */}
          <div data-aos="fade-up-sm" data-aos-offset="0" data-aos-delay="150" class="mt-5 flex items-center justify-start gap-x-6 py-1.5 pt-5">
            <div class="group-hover/item:bg-primary bg-primary/5 flex h-14 w-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg transition duration-300">
              <img
                src="/images/icons/svg/analytics.svg"
                alt="License icon"
                class="h-7 w-7 transition"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-h5 mb-px">持牌经营，合法合规</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">持有马来西亚证券委员会颁发的资本市场服务执照，确保所有财务规划服务均符合监管要求</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          {/* Feature 2 */}
          <div data-aos="fade-up-sm" data-aos-offset="0" data-aos-delay="300" class="mt-5 flex items-center justify-start gap-x-6 py-1.5 pt-5">
            <div class="group-hover/item:bg-primary bg-primary/5 flex h-14 w-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg transition duration-300">
              <img
                src="/images/icons/svg/expertise.svg"
                alt="Experience icon"
                class="h-7 w-7 transition"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-h5 mb-px">18年专业经验</h3>
              <p class="text-sm">自2008年获得许可以来，积累了超过18年的专业财务规划经验，为500+企业提供合规服务</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
